{"tid":2274975,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【校舍翻身】樂善堂小學改裝過渡屋已入伙　受助家庭感欣慰：租平地方大","createTime":"2020-11-06T21:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T02:21:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f35877767b776dc6556ca601143cd9e59bc25ecc","tid":2274975,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T21:29:03.000Z","msg":"今屆政府也積極推動過渡房屋政策，其中九龍城樂善堂小學，去年起改建課室間隔，改變用途為51伙過渡屋，項目命名「樂屋」，主要是2至5人家庭單位，所有住戶本月內入伙。有新遷入住戶難掩喜悅，指居住環境較劏房翻倍，空間更闊落，子女各有私人空間，家人之間相處更和諧，形容「終於似返一頭家」。<br />\n<br />\n即睇陳女士一家三口的改裝單位：<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2795000/2795586/fain1106815_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2795000%2F2795586%2Ffain1106815_1024_1024.jpg&h=54374207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2795000/2795586/fain1106814_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2795000%2F2795586%2Ffain1106814_1024_1024.jpg&h=bb65f4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2795000/2795586/fain1106811_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2795000%2F2795586%2Ffain1106811_1024_1024.jpg&h=5f9f9501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2795000/2795586/fain1106813_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2795000%2F2795586%2Ffain1106813_1024_1024.jpg&h=5a4bfe82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳女士是單親媽媽，照顧14歲大仔及12歲幼女，原本一家3口居於新蒲崗一洋樓劏房，面積僅100呎，月租6,500元，水電雜費千逾元。她形容以前居住環境差，壓迫感重，床褥闊度僅兩呎半，子女沒有固定私人空間，兩兄妹常吵架，令她也隨著波動，「我情緒都受影響，會暴燥。屋企太細，好有壓迫感。」<br />\n<br />\n於疫情下，陳女士原本任職銷售，但近日失業；幸好她舉家9月底搬入「樂屋」，租金支出減少一半。新居原本是半間課室，現時已加裝消防系統及去水渠，有獨立廁所及開放式廚房，子女也有各自的床架及書枱。陳女士稱居住環境明顯改善，子女爭執減少，「個仔有日咁講：搬入來之後，現在才像一頭家，真的感到很幸運很欣慰。」<br />\n<br />\n樂善堂總幹事劉愛詩稱，「樂屋」住戶多來自基層劏房戶，這是全港首間閒置校舍，把26個課室改裝成過渡屋，建築成本約1,544萬元。她稱項目最大特色，包括保留操場作戶外康樂空間，也設共享洗衣廊及圖書角等設施。她形容早前申請反應踴躍，申請期首周就錄得逾500宗申請。機構亦於宋皇臺道，發展下一個組合過渡屋項目。"},{"pid":"6b794e6d05515b6c8b47d6e436476d4199a060ba","tid":2274975,"uid":86360,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T21:34:39.000Z","msg":"睇姿勢仲以為係咩成功人士"},{"pid":"4e691fb992e7edb8662ab585bd87ba867fd4779e","tid":2274975,"uid":130105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T21:35:29.000Z","msg":"點解唔大量整"},{"pid":"8a75eae6dd86a4f7f369046f38fe92ce36ce7d9f","tid":2274975,"uid":358520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b794e6d05515b6c8b47d6e436476d4199a060ba","tid":2274975,"uid":86360,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T21:34:39.000Z","msg":"睇姿勢仲以為係咩成功人士"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T21:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6168af72033065b6f83d0e2ffee2cdaa1fc5f7","tid":2274975,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a75eae6dd86a4f7f369046f38fe92ce36ce7d9f","tid":2274975,"uid":358520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b794e6d05515b6c8b47d6e436476d4199a060ba","tid":2274975,"uid":86360,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T21:34:39.000Z","msg":"睇姿勢仲以為係咩成功人士"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T21:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T21:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos